Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:25.35,EDCN,,0,0,0,,我一定会比那阳光 (Shine! Shine!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:27.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,更加耀眼夺目! (Shine! Shine!)
